å³n&gt;N_1&gt;max(Nï¼Œ[\frac{2M}{\varepsilon}])æ—¶ï¼Œ(\frac{M}{n}&lt; \frac{\varepsilon}{2}ï¼Œn &gt; \frac{2M}{\varepsilon}) <br />
