<br />
\Rightarrow 0\leq b_n-a_n\leq c_n-a_n \Rightarrow \lim_{n\to\infty}{(b_n-a_n)}=0 <br />
<br />
\lim_{b\to\infty}{b_n} = \lim{(b_n - a_n + a_n)} = \lim{a_n} \rightarrow a (n \rightarrow \infty)<br />
\end{array}]</p>

<p><strong>ä¾‹ï¼š</strong></p>

<p>è¯æ˜ $a&gt;1ï¼Œk \in Z^+$ æ—¶ï¼Œ$lim_{n\to\infty}{\frac{n^k}{a^n}}=0$</p>

<p>è¯æ˜å¦‚ä¸‹ï¼š</p>

