\end{array}]</p>

<p><strong>ä¾‹ï¼š</strong></p>

<p>$\forall a&gt;0ï¼Œè¯æ˜\lim_{n\to\infty}{^n\sqrt{a}}=1$</p>

<p>è¯æ˜å¦‚ä¸‹ï¼š</p>

<p>é¦–å…ˆè¯æ˜ $\lim{^n\sqrt{n}}=1$</p>

<p>[\begin{array}{c}
