<br />
\forall \varepsilon &gt; 0ï¼Œå–N=[\frac{4}{\varepsilon ^2}]<br />
<br />
å½“n&gt;Næ—¶ï¼Œæœ‰|n^{\frac{1}{n}}-1|&lt;\frac{2}{\sqrt{n}}&lt;\varepsilon<br />
